<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/10715206-amelia">Amelia</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Not really. The stories focus largely on lust, sex, marriage and love. There is seduction and there is rape. There is cheating and there is incest. Th<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Not really. The stories focus largely on lust, sex, marriage and love. There is seduction and there is rape. There is cheating and there is incest. The Heptameron is not particularly graphic by modern standards, but I wouldn't call it clean.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
