    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4133761445" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer5381073318566757060"><strong>Virtue and corruption </strong><br/><br/>Fascinating read. Interesting stories and pertinent evaluations. On the one hand there is the aspect of human flaws, sinful failings, and base behaviour. On the other, virtue and spiritual inspiration. Marguerite definitely exposes the corruption and predatory sexual nature of the Friars. What a bunch of crooks. It&apos;s no wonder the Roman Catholics condemned her Heptameron as Lutheran in doctrine and immoral. I found it difficult to understand some of the sentences. The synta</span>
  <span id="freeText5381073318566757060" style="display:none"><strong>Virtue and corruption </strong><br /><br />Fascinating read. Interesting stories and pertinent evaluations. On the one hand there is the aspect of human flaws, sinful failings, and base behaviour. On the other, virtue and spiritual inspiration. Marguerite definitely exposes the corruption and predatory sexual nature of the Friars. What a bunch of crooks. It's no wonder the Roman Catholics condemned her Heptameron as Lutheran in doctrine and immoral. I found it difficult to understand some of the sentences. The syntax is unusual. It's translated from old French so no surprise. </span>
  <a data-text-id="5381073318566757060" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

